      "index": 0,
      "url": "about:srcdoc",
      "title": "EduAakashaA - Join as Tutor",
      "bodyText": "EA\nEdu\nAakashaA\nJoin Us\nEduAakashaA\n\nEmpowering students across CBSE and State Boards with personalised one-to-one coaching. We are looking for passionate Tutors and Career Counsellors to join our growing network.\n\nApply Now\nLearn More\n500+\nStudents Enrolled\n50+\nExpert Tutors\n15+\nBoards Covered\n98%\nSatisfaction Rate\n\nWHY EDUAAKASHAA?\n\nBuild your teaching career with us\n\nJoin a platform dedicated to quality education, flexible schedules, and meaningful impact on students futures.\n\n🌎\nReach Students Anywhere\n\nConnect with learners across India through our online and hybrid coaching model for CBSE, ICSE, and all major state boards.\n\n⏰\nFlexible Scheduling\n\nSet your own time slots and availability. Teach when it works for you - mornings, evenings, or weekends.\n\n💰\nCompetitive Compensation\n\nDefine your own hourly fee. We ensure fair, transparent, and timely payments for every session.\n\n📈\nGrow Your Profile\n\nBuild your reputation with student reviews, showcase your expertise, and expand your professional network.\n\n🛠\nTools and Support\n\nAccess our teaching dashboard, content library, scheduling tools, and dedicated support team.\n\n🤝\nCommunity of Educators\n\nCollaborate with fellow tutors and counsellors. Share resources, strategies, and best practices.\n\nOPEN ROLES\n\nWho we are looking for\n\nWhether you are an experienced teacher or a career guidance expert, there is a place for you at EduAakashaA.\n\nTUTOR\nOne-to-One Academic Tutor\nTeach subjects across CBSE and State Board curricula (Classes 1 to 12)\nPersonalised lesson plans for each student\nConduct live sessions via video or in-person\nTrack student progress and share feedback\nUpload your own course content and materials\nCOUNSELLOR\nCareer Counsellor / Mentor\nGuide students on career paths after 10th and 12th\nAptitude assessment and interest mapping\nCollege selection and entrance exam strategies\nOne-to-one mentoring sessions\nHelp students build portfolios and applications\n\nREGISTRATION DETAILS\n\nInformation we will need from you\n\nOur quick registration collects everything needed to set up your tutor or counsellor profile.\n\n👤\n\nFull Name and Contact\n\n🎓\n\nQualifications and Experience\n\n📚\n\nSubjects / Boards Covered\n\n🕐\n\nAvailable Time Slots\n\n💵\n\nFee Per Hour\n\n🔗\n\nLinkedIn Profile URL\n\n📎\n\nSample Course Content\n\n📝\n\nBrief Bio / Intro\n\nREADY TO JOIN?\n\nRegister as an EduAakashaA Tutor / Counsellor\n\nFill out our quick Google Form to express your interest. Our team will review your profile and get back to you within 48 hours.\n\nClick the button below to open the registration form. Enter your details, upload sample course content, and choose your preferred time slots.\n\nOpen Registration Form\n\nPowered by Google Forms - Your data is stored securely\n\nEA\nEdu\nAakashaA\n\n© 2026 EduAakashaA. All rights reserved. | contact@eduaakashaa.com",
